param.string: CASE WHEN $Aggregation.ovrrd_rsdl_mtrty_mnths IS NULL THEN ((@dateDiff(@ASOF_DATE, $Aggregation.dt_mtrty))/365.25) * 12 ELSE $Aggregation.ovrrd_rsdl_mtrty_mnths END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.ovrrd_orgnl_mtrty_mnths IS NULL THEN ((@dateDiff($Aggregation.dt_strt, $Aggregation.dt_mtrty))/365.25) * 12 ELSE $Aggregation.ovrrd_orgnl_mtrty_mnths END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.ovrrd_instr_rsdl_mtrty_mnths IS NULL THEN ((@dateDiff(@ASOF_DATE, $Aggregation.dt_instr_mtrty))/365.25) * 12 ELSE $Aggregation.ovrrd_instr_rsdl_mtrty_mnths END
CASE WHEN $eu_cr_exposure.ovrrd_nxt_rst_dt_mnths IS NULL THEN ((@dateDiff(@ASOF_DATE, $eu_cr_exposure.dt_nxt_rst))/365.25) * 12 ELSE $eu_cr_exposure.ovrrd_nxt_rst_dt_mnths END
CASE WHEN $eu_cr_exposure.ovrrd_undrlyng_rsdl_mtrty_mnth IS NULL THEN ((@dateDiff(@ASOF_DATE, $eu_cr_exposure.dt_undrlyng_mtrty))/365.25) * 12 ELSE $eu_cr_exposure.ovrrd_undrlyng_rsdl_mtrty_mnth END
CASE WHEN $eu_cr_exposure.ovrrd_ifi_rsdl_mtrty_yrs IS NULL THEN @isNull((@dateDiff(@ASOF_DATE, $eu_cr_exposure.dt_ifi_mtrty)), 0)/365.25 ELSE $eu_cr_exposure.ovrrd_ifi_rsdl_mtrty_yrs END
CASE WHEN $central_government.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_st IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $central_government.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_st ELSE 7 END

CASE  WHEN @isNull($Aggregation.enm_hrct_clss, '') != '' THEN 		         CASE  				 WHEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_lt IN (1,2,3,4,5,6,7) AND $counterparty.cntry_incrprtn_ccy_code != $Aggregation.orgnl_ccy_code THEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_lt 				 WHEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_lt IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_lt                  				 ELSE 7  				 END WHEN @isNull($Aggregation.enm_hrct_clss, '') = '' THEN                  CASE 				 WHEN $Aggregation.ovrrd_enm_instr_cqs_lt IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $Aggregation.ovrrd_enm_instr_cqs_lt 				 WHEN $Aggregation.use_prty_rtng_ind = 'Y' AND $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_lt IN (1,2,3,4,5,6,7) AND $counterparty.cntry_incrprtn_ccy_code != $Aggregation.orgnl_ccy_code THEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_lt 				 WHEN $Aggregation.use_prty_rtng_ind = 'Y' AND $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_lt IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_lt 				 ELSE 7 				 END ELSE 7 END
CASE WHEN $central_government.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_lt IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $central_government.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_lt ELSE 7 END

CASE  WHEN @isNull($Aggregation.enm_hrct_clss, '') != '' THEN                  CASE  				 WHEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_st IN (1,2,3,4,5,6,7) AND $counterparty.cntry_incrprtn_ccy_code != $Aggregation.orgnl_ccy_code THEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_st 				 WHEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_st IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_st                  				 ELSE 7  				 END WHEN @isNull($Aggregation.enm_hrct_clss, '') = '' THEN                  CASE 				 WHEN $Aggregation.ovrrd_enm_instr_cqs_st IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $Aggregation.ovrrd_enm_instr_cqs_st 				 WHEN $Aggregation.use_prty_rtng_ind = 'Y' AND $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_st IN (1,2,3,4,5,6,7) AND $counterparty.cntry_incrprtn_ccy_code != $Aggregation.orgnl_ccy_code THEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_st 				 WHEN $Aggregation.use_prty_rtng_ind = 'Y' AND $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_st IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $counterparty.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_st 				 ELSE 7 				 END ELSE 7 END

CASE  WHEN $Aggregation.ovrrd_enm_instr_cqs_lt IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $Aggregation.ovrrd_enm_instr_cqs_lt WHEN $Aggregation.use_prty_rtng_ind = 'Y' AND $issuer.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_lt IN (1,2,3,4,5,6,7) AND $issuer.cntry_incrprtn_ccy_code != $Aggregation.orgnl_ccy_code THEN $issuer.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_lt  WHEN $Aggregation.use_prty_rtng_ind = 'Y' AND $issuer.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_lt IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $issuer.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_lt  	      	   ELSE 7  END

CASE  WHEN $Aggregation.ovrrd_enm_instr_cqs_st IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $Aggregation.ovrrd_enm_instr_cqs_st WHEN $Aggregation.use_prty_rtng_ind = 'Y' AND $issuer.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_st IN (1,2,3,4,5,6,7) AND $issuer.cntry_incrprtn_ccy_code != $Aggregation.orgnl_ccy_code THEN $issuer.ovrrd_enm_frgn_cqs_st  WHEN $Aggregation.use_prty_rtng_ind = 'Y' AND $issuer.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_st IN (1,2,3,4,5,6) THEN $issuer.ovrrd_enm_prty_cqs_st  	      	   ELSE 7  END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.enm_mtrty_mthd='TRNCH_FNL_MTRTY' AND $Aggregation.dt_trnch_mtrty IS NOT NULL THEN (@dateDiff(@ASOF_DATE, $Aggregation.dt_trnch_mtrty))/365.25 END

CASE WHEN $entity.apply_sa_rw_mthd_ind = 'Y' THEN @isNull($Aggregation.enm_rw_mthd, 'STANDARDISED') WHEN @isNull($entity.apply_sa_rw_mthd_ind, '') != 'Y' THEN @isNull($Aggregation.enm_irb_rw_mthd, @isNull($Aggregation.enm_rw_mthd, 'STANDARDISED')) END
